name: 0004 meditation
description: This collection of cards is made for a planet from another universe, they deal with experiences of our lives so that beings from the distant planet can visualize those experiences by scanning the barcode of the cards, with a part of their body similar to the third eye. . . . . . . . . our. In this way, beings will be able to add our experience to their life experience, so that in many cases they do not make the same mistakes ... The being who contacted me through a dream, so that I could write these letters, told me that I was the "Loco de Grecia", that's why this collection is called like that.
